# https://github.com/elisabettacaterina/CRMvr/V18_Transparency_Inference_Making
<https://github.com/elisabettacaterina/CRMvr/V18_Transparency_Inference_Making> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
