<https://github.com/elisabettacaterina/CRMvr/V18_Transparency_Inference_Making> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "This class comprises the action of making propositions and statements about particular geometrical or morphological representations of an V4 Find, its possible virtual representations (V6 3D Find), V17 sources and 3D objects. It includes evaluations and interpretations based on sources available for 3D reconstructions with the aim to fill the gap between documentation and 3D model obtained from them."@en .
<https://github.com/elisabettacaterina/CRMvr/V18_Transparency_Inference_Making> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "V18 Transparency Inference Making"@en .
