<https://github.com/elisabettacaterina/CRMvr/V20_Accuracy_Evaluation> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "This class comprises the action of make propositions on data observable from a V17 Source or E31 Document by making evaluations based on the V22 Accuracy Grade of informations on morphological and geometrical representations of the Cultural Heritage or Immaterial Heritage that it is possible to digitally reproduce."@en .
<https://github.com/elisabettacaterina/CRMvr/V20_Accuracy_Evaluation> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "V20 Accuracy Evaluation"@en .
